Subsequent to the merger, DMCCB Bank N.A. was merged into HSBC Bank Nevada, N.A. The purchase price paid by HSBC Finance Corporation for the fair value of assets and liabilities of DMCCB Bank, N.A., including Cardholder relationships has been "pushed down" and recorded on HSBC Bank Nevada N.A. financial statements. Fair value, paid by HSBC Finance Corporation in excess of the assets acquired and liabilities assumed has not been pushed down to HSBC Bank Nevada, N.A. and remains at the parent company. These fair value adjustments represent preliminary estimates and are subject to further adjustments as additional information, appraisals and other valuation data are available/obtained.
